  "unavailable_fields": {
    "per_cell_voltage_array_byte_map": "CanZE polls each cell with a separate DID 0x9021..0x907C; per-cell DID lookup table is in CanZE source (https://github.com/fluffyfreak/CANZE) but offsets vary per cell. Implement by enumerating that range and reading each as uint16 mV.",
    "charge_port_temperature": "Not documented.",
